CHAT HISTORY UI UPDATE LOG
==========================
Date: 2025-01-19

CHANGES MADE:
1. Modified the "New Chat" button to be icon-only
   - Changed from full button with text to icon button
   - Uses outline variant
   - Shows only the Plus icon
   - Added title="New chat" for tooltip

2. Added "Delete All" button
   - Icon-only button with Trash2 icon
   - Outline variant with destructive (red) hover color
   - Disabled when no sessions or loading
   - Has double confirmation for safety
   - Added title="Delete all chats" for tooltip

3. Layout changes:
   - Both buttons are now compact icon buttons
   - They fit nicely next to the search bar and filter button
   - All within the 3/4 width constraint

CODE CHANGES:
From:
```jsx
{/* New Chat Button */}
<Button
  onClick={handleCreateNewChat}
  size="sm"
  className="gap-2 flex-shrink-0"
>
  <Plus className="h-4 w-4" />
  New Chat
</Button>
```

To:
```jsx
{/* New Chat Button */}
<Button
  onClick={handleCreateNewChat}
  size="icon"
  variant="outline"
  className="flex-shrink-0"
  title="New chat"
>
  <Plus className="h-4 w-4" />
</Button>

{/* Delete All Button */}
<Button
  onClick={handleDeleteAllSessions}
  size="icon"
  variant="outline"
  className="flex-shrink-0 text-destructive hover:text-destructive"
  disabled={loading || filteredSessions.length === 0}
  title="Delete all chats"
>
  <Trash2 className="h-4 w-4" />
</Button>
```

TESTING:
- Navigate to http://localhost:3000/chat-history
- Look for the new icon buttons next to the search bar
- The layout should show: [Search bar] [Filter icon] [+ icon] [Trash icon]
- All buttons should be the same height and style

TROUBLESHOOTING:
- Hard refresh the page (Ctrl+F5)
- Clear browser cache
- Check browser console for the log message
- Container has been rebuilt with --no-cache